  "title": "Sales Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Provide support to the sales team, including Business Development Executives and Managers, in sales and marketing activities.</li><li>Prepare sales quotations and follow up with customers accordingly.</li><li>Manage order processing and generate all required documentation.</li><li>Plan, coordinate, and monitor shipment schedules to ensure on-time delivery to customers.</li><li>Pack shipments and prepare all necessary shipping documents.</li><li>Manage and handle Letters of Credit (LC) documents for submission.</li><li>Coordinate with freight forwarders regarding shipment arrangements.</li><li>Update sales forecasts and prepare monthly sales reports on outstanding orders at month-end.</li><li>Maintain and update the sales database and document library.</li></ul>",
